file_content.text: The ghost cell hasn't come for its delivery yet. I assume that fits your plan?
Well... there's still stuff here. Guess the ghost cell hasn't picked up its delivery.
Get the crates open and climb inside. We're taking a ride.
We can hide in these.
There's plenty of room inside these things. Guess where we're going?
Our ticket to the village.
At least our eyes adjust to the dark.
Worst part is, I've traveled this way before....
Get in. Anyone else opens the crate, shoot them.
Time for a dangerous journey.
We'll be ready. Let's hope it doesn't come to that.
I'll cozy up to my blaster. See you on the other side.
[This is a large crate of engineering supplies and construction materials. There's easily enough room for one or more people to fit inside.]
[Climb into the crate.]
[Leave the crate alone.]
[You leave the crate alone.]
